            <p class="indentboth">
                <strong>Regency Plastics</strong> has been one of North America's largest extruders and converters of polyethylene sheeting and packaging for almost 60 years.
                Traditional values and the utmost attention to details have resulted in numerous long-term relationships with many of North America's
                leading manufacturers and retailers, as well as securing us as a major supplier to the construction industry with our CGP <!--and CGSB--> Vapour
                Barrier films.
            </p>
            <p class="indentboth">
                <strong>Regency Plastics</strong> is ISO 9001 accredited and our products are FDA/IMS, and HACCP and GHP certified.
                Our customer service representatives work closely with all areas of production and sales to ensure manufacturing accuracy 
                and on-time delivery.
            </p>
